{"tid":529164,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]一人一首歌最能代表你最近經歷/心情 放低你既心事","createTime":"2018-01-14T14:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T17:18:36.000Z","uid":18894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"281c71ed2fc93ca882589fe5a5c5645e55c8c9b9","tid":529164,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:49:22.000Z","msg":"我唔後悔識到你同愛上你 <br />\n如果比我揀多次 我都係會選擇愛上你<br />\n雖然我唔知你到底係心入面有冇鍾意過我 你亦都無講過任何一句「我愛你」<br />\n但我過程中好開心  無時無刻陪住大家 傾我地既未來<br />\n最後連朋友都做唔到 因為我怕我會放唔低你<br />\n其實我好想講一句<br />\n 「我好掛住你」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_e48u7oxqA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_e48u7oxqA8&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=759f468d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_e48u7oxqA8</a><br />\n<br />\n陶喆 - 普通朋友<br />\n<br />\n等待　我隨時隨地在等待　做妳感情上的依賴<br />\n我沒有任何的疑問　這是愛<br />\n<br />\n我猜　妳早就想要說明白　我覺得自己好失敗<br />\n從天堂掉落到深淵　多無奈<br />\n<br />\n我願意改變 (what can I do)<br />\n重新再來一遍 (just give me chance)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我無法只是普通朋友　感情已那麼深　叫我怎麼能放手<br />\n<br />\n但妳說　I only wanna be your friend　做個朋友<br />\n我在妳心中只是 just a friend　不是情人<br />\n我感激妳對我這樣的坦白　但我給妳的愛暫時收不回來</span><br />\nSo I 我不能只是 be your friend　I just can't be your friend<br />\n<br />\nno,no,no,我不能只是做妳的朋友　不能做普通朋友"},{"pid":"7732b6fcb7aa60741a983131ba46f971163585cf","tid":529164,"uid":148042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-SIHSEHc0S8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-SIHSEHc0S8&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=08fef09c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-SIHSEHc0S8</a><br />\n<br />\n陳僖儀 Sita Chan - 忘川<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf9179a469094a8e58bb0234204114d754837ad","tid":529164,"uid":42328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GYvTbLvbrAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGYvTbLvbrAY&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dd385fe0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GYvTbLvbrAY</a><br />\n<br />\n用了一支煙的時間 掛念誰<br />\n浪費了幾分鐘的感情 計算得到還未算太累<br />\n而你似看穿我 扮強悍<br />\n笑我姿勢未純熟 吸了煙 呼出眼淚"},{"pid":"c0c83776fc73d4ce68af632f7ce9c68837d776db","tid":529164,"uid":86208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:10:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zOEISgh7k_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzOEISgh7k_g&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5c3dcd3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zOEISgh7k_g</a><br />\n說散就散<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb29aa15d3e1fa219a9f96491fcecdcb30ed3f","tid":529164,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7732b6fcb7aa60741a983131ba46f971163585cf","tid":529164,"uid":148042,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-SIHSEHc0S8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-SIHSEHc0S8&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=08fef09c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-SIHSEHc0S8</a><br />\n<br />\n陳僖儀 Sita Chan - 忘川<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:12:43.000Z","msg":"巴打有咩故事"},{"pid":"92afd558177f868eac1e1414e87737f026476e6c","tid":529164,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T15:15:23.000Z","msg"