75b4361de308f52b7389ef1ac5187a","tid":529164,"uid":7117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"擦光所有火柴難令氣氛像從前閃耀<br />\n至少感激當日陪着我開甜蜜的玩笑"},{"pid":"a32e12c2479fd1a728598e504f0589885053aba6","tid":529164,"uid":44493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"一隻歌會唔會太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g-E0ojfjYu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg-E0ojfjYu0&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f2c5d8f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g-E0ojfjYu0</a><br />\n<br />\n又一遍     我忘記了是哪些事件<br />\n妳言詞閃爍     原因當然不明顯<br />\n試著看見     讓時間倒轉回到從前<br />\n認真如我     有抓不到的邊緣<br />\n <br />\n在想像的空間不斷排迴<br />\n那畫面永遠明確<br />\n就算是閉上眼     也無法否決"},{"pid":"d33fcf1d8e5204d6c7d6abc7350fef93a8dc2884","tid":529164,"uid":71154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:24:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uAC1hJxRHAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuAC1hJxRHAI&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=09c8e6fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uAC1hJxRHAI</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我不願離開這公司<br />\n全都因為對你太鍾意"},{"pid":"2ec71eff8f55442264a3fd397f40ca3e90793711","tid":529164,"uid":18894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a32e12c2479fd1a728598e504f0589885053aba6","tid":529164,"uid":44493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"一隻歌會唔會太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g-E0ojfjYu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg-E0ojfjYu0&d=q9Wwmv23EBxp2Y95bqwzLzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f2c5d8f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g-E0ojfjYu0</a><br />\n<br />\n又一遍     我忘記了是哪些事件<br />\n妳言詞閃爍     原因當然不明顯<br />\n試